      "name": "Two-Handed",
      "nameKo": "양손",
      "description": "A Two-Handed weapon requires two hands when you attack with it.",
      "descriptionKo": "양손 무기는 공격할 때 두 손이 필요합니다."
    },
    {
      "id": "versatile",
